### Variables

@baseUrl = https://bookmarkhive.test
@contentType = application/json


### List own tags

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}


### Create tag

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/tags
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "name": "Test Tag"
}


