### Get own tag

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/tags/test-tag
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}


### Edit own tag

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/tags/first-tag
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "name": "Updated Title"
}


### Delete own tag

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/tags/test-tag
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}


### List public tags of a user

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/{username}/tags


### Get public tag

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/{username}/tags/test-tag


